Author: ParticularlyPigeon
Text: I'm so sorry to hear that. I hate it when I can't sleep because having that free time makes me more likely to binge. :( But, recently I've gotten myself so exhausted that I'll sleep for like 10 hours a night, and it's great because I barely have time to eat between sleep and work and anything else I need to do.

Author: AsianMemes
Text: I hate having insomnia because it gives me more time to break down and binge late at night
